data.description: This beautiful home located in the desirable Nautica Community offers a open concept design with a abundance of natural light throughout the home. The owners have not only taken meticulous care of the home but have replaced the roof in 2021. The HVAC, security system, Irrigation System and salt water pool finish are all brand new. The guest bathroom has  also been refurbished. The back yard is large and offers a spacious patio that over looks the pool and spa. With 4 bedrooms 3 bathrooms and 2,179 sq.ft. this home offers a abundance of living space. The Luxurious master retreat boasts a coffered ceiling , walk in closet, a soaking tub, a walk-in shower and dual sinks . The home comes complete with accordion shutters. Nautica offers a resort lifestyle including a Clubhouse, Fitness Center, Pool and Tennis. Located close to shopping, dinning, entertainment and A rated schools.
